{
  "uuid": "9baa808856e9d26efaa8d48b66e2dcd0",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Delivery Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Apparel Company Hiring</strong><br /><strong>Delivery Driver + Warehouse Assistant</strong></p><p>We are an established apparel company with <strong>over 20 years of operations</strong> looking for a <strong>Delivery Driver cum Warehouse Assistant</strong> to join our team on a long-term basis.</p><p><strong>Working Hours</strong></p><ul><li><p>5-day work week</p></li><li><p>Monday – Friday</p></li><li><p>9:00am – 6:00pm</p></li></ul><p><strong>Location</strong></p><ul><li><p>Warehouse at <strong>Upper Thomson – 9 Tagore Lane</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Salary & Benefits</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>$2,100 – $2,500 per month (before CPF)</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Yearly performance bonus</strong></p></li><li><p>Employee benefits included (insurance, annual leave, etc.)</p></li><li><p><strong>Company vehicle provided</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diesel & CashCard fully paid by company</p></li><li><p>Vehicle <strong>cannot be driven home</strong></p></li></ul></li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li><p>Delivery of apparel products to chain retail stores across Singapore</p></li><li><p>Up to <strong>12 delivery points per day</strong></p></li><li><p>Routes are <strong>planned and zoned properly</strong></p></li><li><p>Assist with warehouse duties such as packing, sorting, and stock-taking</p></li><li><p>Loading and unloading of goods</p></li><li><p>Product arrangement at outlets</p></li></ul><p><strong>Workload & Schedule Clarity</strong></p><ul><li><p>Deliveries are completed <strong>within working hours</strong></p></li><li><p>Completion depends on driver efficiency, but <strong>all drivers are generally able to complete on time</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>No overtime required</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Physical Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Role involves <strong>moderate lifting and handling of apparel cartons</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Valid Singapore <strong>Class 3 or Class 3A driving licence</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Minimum 1 year of driving experience</strong></p></li><li><p>Able to navigate using Google Maps / Waze</p></li><li><p>Responsible, punctual, and able to work independently</p></li></ul><p><strong>Who Can Apply</strong></p><ul><li><p>Singaporeans, PRs, and eligible candidates welcome</p></li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><ul><li><p>Stable, long-term role</p></li><li><p>Established company with over 20 years of track record</p></li><li><p>Structured routes and reasonable workload</p></li><li><p>Performance-based rewards</p></li></ul><p><strong>How to Apply</strong><br />Interested candidates, please WhatsApp <strong>Felix at 9780 9447</strong> with:</p><ul><li><p>Full Name</p></li><li><p>Residential Location</p></li><li><p>Earliest Start Date</p></li><li><p>Driving Experience</p></li></ul><p>Selected applicants will be contacted to arrange an interview.</p>",
